[MOTION_PHILOSOPHY]
- Everything moves slightly, nothing is static
- Motion is slow, intentional, weightless

[BACKGROUND]
- Grid: fixed
- Particles: drift slowly (very low speed)
- Connections: subtle fade in/out

[HERO_TEXT]
- Main heading: slight parallax on mouse move
- Ghost text: ultra slow horizontal drift

[3D_CURSOR]
- Soft circular cursor follower
- Lagged movement (lerp, not direct)

[RIGHT_PANEL]
- Float animation: sin(time) based (very subtle)
- Slight tilt on mouse move

[STATS_CARDS]
- Hover = lift + glow
- No aggressive scaling

[SCROLL]
- Camera illusion (depth shift), not just translateY